dct_title_s: Index, assessment maps, Borough of East Rutherford, Bergen County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map showing waterways: Hackensack River, Berry's Creek, Ackerman's Creek, and Fish Creek as they relate to the properties and roadways in the Meadowlands area of East Rutherford, New Jersey
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Year is inferred by revision notes; main year on map is 1931; however there are revisions listed up until 1964.
